{"tid":2361320,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解含登力會覺得侵侵最後唔會絕地反擊","createTime":"2021-01-10T14:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T08:23:25.000Z","uid":209890,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9bf6d9c1fc102f6e4eb37bedf28b09c2ced9ea","tid":2361320,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:08:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">趕狗入窮巷必遭反噬</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原本我都覺得侵侵依幾日無動作<br />\n應該都唔會再有動作<br />\n因為之後打法律戰 其實好多案都告佢唔入<br />\n但依加既情況睇得出民主黨係想佢消失係美國<br />\n封殺佢家族 佢本人 要佢坐監 要佢死係監獄<br />\n加上五角大樓出聲 侵侵依然有兵權<br />\n未來依3日就係絕對關鍵<br />\n趕狗入窮巷必遭反噬<br />\n侵侵會係你出手殺佢之前先出手消滅你<br />\n物極必反都唔識<br />\n得番10日大家好黎好去咪得囉<br />\n反正你都大權在手<br />\n係都要做到共產黨咁<br />\n依加民兵已經唔會在乎侵侵係咪當選<br />\n佢地依加目標係反左膠<br />\n而你係出唔到軍隊阻止佢地<br />\n因為20號前你唔係總統呀<br />\n今獲你等收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a5a464ae8fceb3e1ef027e5c6dc7022f49ed50","tid":2361320,"uid":371953,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"我都想,但應該都唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263568906bc85eb5570a87df9981f257436a4cfa","tid":2361320,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7k0dHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7k0dHJ.jpg&h=6022f8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16d474b95678aab1b77b3ab961bb4c661ebea6e","tid":2361320,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"263568906bc85eb5570a87df9981f257436a4cfa","tid":2361320,"uid":324629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m7k0dHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm7k0dHJ.jpg&h=6022f8f7&s=